            "description": "Generates and downloads a QR code for the restaurant. The QR code points to the public menu URL.\n\n**Query Parameters:**\n- size: S, M, L, or XL (default: M)\n- format: PNG or SVG (default: PNG)\n- includeLogo: true/false (default: false)\n- foregroundColor: optional hex (e.g. #000000)\n- backgroundColor: optional hex (e.g. #FFFFFF)\n\n**Note:** SVG format is not yet implemented. Use PNG for now.\n\n**Error Correction Level:** H (30%)\n\n**URL Format:** https://{domain}/m/{slug}"
          }
